pan> 说: 在HTML文件里引用其他JS文件的前面先定义全局变量试试看？像这样：<br><script type='text/javascript'>var bar;</script><br><script type='te...</q></div>可以了，谢谢！<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/02.gif\" smileid=\"41\" alt=\"(bgm25)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/09/200970.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1329126","time":"2018-3-19 15:14","userId":"qq624130658","userName":"老悠","userSign":"(无聊了可以进二次元儿黑屁群玩玩，678621887 ...)","message":"不是把相关的js统一引用到html文件里吗","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/02/41/24149.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1329130","time":"2018-3-19 15:22","userId":"henix","userName":"henix","userSign":"","message":"你这样写的确会 undefined 的，因为 script 加载的脚本的执行跟后面的 js 的执行顺序不能保证一定是谁先谁后的。也就是说先执行了后面的 js ，所以找不到。<br>现在 js 的模块标准都用 webpack 了，不过配置起来比较复杂。最简单的方法应该就是在 html 里直接引用多个 js ，比如把你的公共函数放到一个 lib.js 里：<br><div class=\"codeHighlight\"><pre><script src=\"lib.js\"></script><br><script><br>// 这里使用 lib.js 里定义的函数<br></script></pre></div>","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/76/7650.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1329139","time":"2018-3-19 15:29","userId":"iiiiuuuu","userName":"完全没有","userSign":"(就是没有)","message":"复制，粘贴<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/02/68/26866.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1329170","time":"2018-3-19 18:48","userId":"hc","userName":"月火","userSign":"(おのれ！これで勝ったと思うなよぉ!!! ...)","message":"一般来说不是用node那些framework吗?<br>为什么要这样在html引用?<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/13.gif\" smileid=\"52\" alt=\"(bgm36)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/03/74/37469.jpg","floor":"#7-1","id":"1329172","time":"2018-3-19 18:52","userId":"fantasy","userName":"fantasy","userSign":"","message":"＋1"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/08/95/89561.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1329171","time":"2018-3-19 18:51","userId":"upsuper","userName":"upsuper","userSign":"","message":"可以用es6 module（虽然Firefox的支持还要再等两个月……）","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/78/177820.jpg","floor":"#8-1","id":"1329390","tim